Container.Overview:
This is a 100% inline bot, you can't talk directly to him, you need to add your bot to your telegram and in any chat you type this:
@BOT_NAME NAME_OF_THE_MOVIE

And this will show you 5 movies that you can download click on the and will send the name and the image of the movie on a message so you can send to a friend or in my case my wife.

Container.Description:
With this container you will be able to ask for the bot for movies via telegram, and a message is sent to the chat you is asking for the bot, making easy to tell your friend when you are downloading a movie to watch together.
  
